  - type matching
  - serialize props
  - deserialize props
  - optional command aliases/capabilities
- Move all menu metadata into a registry or table (even if static C++).
- Introduce a stable `IWindowStateCodec` interface.

Plugin-point opportunities
- `window_type_registry` is already the strongest plugin seam (`app/window_type_registry.h` / `.cpp`).
- Expand it to include persistence and menu metadata before building a full plugin system.

