- Risks
  - Workspace compatibility regressions (`app/test_pattern_app.cpp` workspace load/save logic spans lines 3476-4464).
  - Window ID stability regressions (`findWindowById`/registry maps in `app/test_pattern_app.cpp` lines ~970-1120).
  - Divergent command behavior between IPC direct commands and registry commands (`app/api_ipc.cpp` vs `app/command_registry.cpp`).
  - UI chrome/frame toggle regressions in frameless windows (`TFrameAnimationWindow` and `TFigletTextWindow`).
- Tests to add
  - `workspace_roundtrip_test`: save/load/save stable subset for `frame_player`, `gallery`, `figlet_text`, `paint`.
