- Grouping recommendation (high value)
  - Split command handlers by domain:
    - `commands_windows.cpp` (`cascade`, `tile`, `close_all`, `window_shadow`, `window_title`)
    - `commands_workspace.cpp` (`save_workspace`, `open_workspace`)
    - `commands_desktop.cpp` (`desktop_*`)
    - `commands_figlet.cpp` (`figlet_*`, `list_figlet_fonts`, `preview_figlet`)
    - `commands_paint.cpp` (`paint_*`, `open_paint_file`)
    - `commands_terminal.cpp` (`terminal_*`)
